    - target: {fileID: 114591927686108806, guid: ee8ad5531e02f4f0eb2d4187ec62c699, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "This is a stream of fluid that generates a puddle and tiny splashes
        when it hits a ground plane. The stream is made up of particles that are
        spawned very close together. \n\nThere is an additional particle system with
        hidden particles which have the same settings as the stream but with fewer
        particles spawned. These are used to spawn the puddles and drops when they
        collide with a collision plane."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
