    - target: {fileID: 114591927686108806, guid: ee8ad5531e02f4f0eb2d4187ec62c699, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: This effects portrays a projectile hitting some sort of organic substance.
        A decal is spawned at the hit point (in this case, simulated by a random
        particle spawn point). There is a particle system for the goop mist, and
