    - target: {fileID: 114591927686108806, guid: ee8ad5531e02f4f0eb2d4187ec62c699, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "This effect is made of a few particle systems with sub emitters. The
        raindrop uses a particle with a render-mode set to \u2018none\u2019 and a
        trail. When the raindrop hits the ground plane it spawns the water ripple
        effect which is a small horizontal billboard which scales up over time to
        simulate a water ripple. \r\nAt the same time as the ripple a small impact
        splash is created which uses a mesh in a cone shape to simulate a circular
        splash.\r\n"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
