    - target: {fileID: 114591927686108806, guid: ee8ad5531e02f4f0eb2d4187ec62c699, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: This effect is made of 4 different particle systems. One system is for
        the explosion which is using a sprite sheet animation. Another system handles
        the shock wave and electrical effects. Finally, there is a system for the
        embers which makes use of the 'radial' option in the velocity module. This
        forces particles away or towards the center point of the particle system.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
